Look, look! Flash me a smile! Smile!

503
00:19:27,901 --> 00:19:28,901
Oh!

504
00:19:29,726 --> 00:19:30,960
Don’t be afraid, Kuya!

505
00:19:30,985 --> 00:19:35,756
Her ancestors are vampires,
that’s why.

506
00:19:35,781 --> 00:19:38,049
Yeah. But she’s a human now.
Purely human.

507
00:19:38,593 --> 00:19:42,252
The third one,
I wanna get to know!

508
00:19:42,717 --> 00:19:44,584
My brother’s missus!

509
00:19:45,201 --> 00:19:47,848
Kuya, kuya Brando.
Please don’t be shocked,

510
00:19:48,500 --> 00:19:50,113
but she’s my girlfriend.

511
00:19:50,493 --> 00:19:51,758
- That’s her!
- That’s her!

512
00:19:52,222 --> 00:19:54,771
- 29… she’s twenty years old!
- Missus?

513
00:19:54,961 --> 00:19:56,948
She just has corduroy for skin,
that’s why she looks like that.

514
00:19:56,973 --> 00:19:57,973
Granny, you too?!

515
00:19:57,998 --> 00:20:00,351
Of course! Why?
Don’t you believe me?

516
00:20:01,286 --> 00:20:02,286
Oh!

517
00:20:02,295 --> 00:20:03,295
What?!

518
00:20:06,506 --> 00:20:09,746
Goldiblocks Love Story: Sophia’s Ensaymada

519
00:20:10,321 --> 00:20:11,321
Action!

520
00:20:17,424 --> 00:20:19,564
“It’s not you, it’s me.”?

521
00:20:25,399 --> 00:20:27,606
Hi, may I share the table?

522
00:20:29,123 --> 00:20:31,190
Of course you can, go ahead.

523
00:20:33,230 --> 00:20:34,310
By the way, my name is Andrei.

524
00:20:34,648 --> 00:20:36,419
- Sophia.
- Nice to meet you.

525
00:20:36,444 --> 00:20:38,118
And because you shared
a seat with me,

526
00:20:38,980 --> 00:20:40,481
I’ll share something with you, too!

527
00:20:41,886 --> 00:20:43,712
Goldiblocks Ensaymada!

528
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:46,967
Wow, thanks!

529
00:20:48,388 --> 00:20:49,388
What is the meaning of this?!

530
00:20:50,448 --> 00:20:51,514
Cut, cut!

531
00:20:51,627 --> 00:20:52,794
I’m sorry, Direk!

532
00:20:52,838 --> 00:20:54,324
Did I do something wrong?

533
00:20:54,629 --> 00:20:55,629
Did I do something wrong?

534
00:20:55,968 --> 00:20:57,022
No, not you!

535
00:20:57,649 --> 00:20:59,656
What is this, Kabo?!

536
00:20:59,733 --> 00:21:01,180
Um, yes, Direk?

537
00:21:01,779 --> 00:21:03,286
What is the matter with you!

538
00:21:03,948 --> 00:21:06,508
Look at our props! It’s moldy!

539
00:21:06,868 --> 00:21:09,455
You’re making me crazy!
Don’t we have a back-up of this?!

540
00:21:09,584 --> 00:21:11,971
We don’t, unfortunately.
We only have a piece of that.

541
00:21:12,161 --> 00:21:13,508
Son of a b..

542
00:21:14,576 --> 00:21:16,076
what the heck are we
going to do about this?!

543
00:21:16,126 --> 00:21:17,441
Ah, Direk? Direk!

544
00:21:18,257 --> 00:21:19,416
- Direk!
- Yes?

545
00:21:19,649 --> 00:21:23,429
Um, with all due respect,
I may have a solution for that.

546
00:21:23,538 --> 00:21:24,718
You have a solution?

547
00:21:24,743 --> 00:21:25,743
Yes, Direk.

548
00:21:26,108 --> 00:21:27,108
Let me handle this.

549
00:21:28,829 --> 00:21:29,829
Are you sure?

550
00:21:29,854 --> 00:21:31,327
Yes…yes, Direk.

551
00:21:31,352 --> 00:21:33,670
- Are you for real?
- Yes, Direk. Let me fix this.

552
00:21:34,750 --> 00:21:35,856
Are you really going to?

553
00:21:35,881 --> 00:21:37,874
I’ll take care of it, just
give me a moment.

554
00:21:38,336 --> 00:21:39,336
See? Look at that!

555
00:21:39,344 --> 00:21:42,377
Kabo, don’t you ever use your head?!
It’s a good thing someone volunteered!

556
00:21:42,703 --> 00:21:43,703
I’m sorry.

557
00:21:43,728 --> 00:21:44,816
Goodness, gracious!

558
00:21:44,841 --> 00:21:45,841
Brother!

559
00:21:49,061 --> 00:21:50,374
I knew it!

560
00:21:51,578 --> 00:21:53,344
None of those three women
are your girlfriend!

561
00:21:53,877 --> 00:21:54,877
Yes, Kuya!

562
00:21:55,650 --> 00:21:56,877
I confess!

563
00:21:56,902 --> 00:21:59,040
You didn’t tell me that
Mariposa is your girlfriend!

564
00:21:59,065 --> 00:22:00,065
What?!

565
00:22:00,090 --> 00:22:03,137
Baby! Come here, baby!

566
00:22:03,174 --> 00:22:05,914
Baby, you don’t have
to deny it anymore.

567
00:22:05,939 --> 00:22:11,104
I told Brando everything about us!

568
00:22:11,129 --> 00:22:12,248
You told him everything?

569
00:22:12,273 --> 00:22:13,273
Yeah!

570
00:22:13,298 --> 00:22:15,926
You told him everything.
She told him everything.

571
00:22:16,106 --> 00:22:18,066
She told him everything.

572
00:22:19,841 --> 00:22:21,994
I thought you told me
you were going to confess?

573
00:22:22,312 --> 00:22:23,312
He…

574
00:22:24,515 --> 00:22:25,832
He is g–

575
00:22:25,857 --> 00:22:26,857
ay!

576
00:22:26,882 --> 00:22:27,882
Gay?!

577
00:22:29,082 --> 00:22:30,396
No… um… Kuya.

578
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,866
The ones coming
after me are gays.

579
00:22:32,951 --> 00:22:34,072
- Yeah! That’s it!
- You know

580
00:22:34,097 --> 00:22:35,793
- how it is when you’re handsome.
- Yes!

581
00:22:35,954 --> 00:22:37,821
I’m basically a gay magnet.

582
00:22:37,846 --> 00:22:42,699
That’s why I have decided Mariposa and I
are going to try getting pregnant!

583
00:22:42,724 --> 00:22:45,075
So they will stop chasing me…

584
00:22:45,100 --> 00:22:46,355
Brother, that’s good news!

585
00:22:46,380 --> 00:22:47,380
That’s great!
Yes!

586
00:22:48,528 --> 00:22:49,629
- What?
- Kiss! Kiss!

587
00:22:49,661 --> 00:22:51,375
- Kiss!
- Maybe later,

588
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:53,093
- when it’s just the two of us left!
- Oh, come on!

589
00:22:53,118 --> 00:22:54,373
- You’re too strong!
- Okay, okay!

590
00:22:54,398 --> 00:22:55,656
Watch it, my strap is –

591
00:22:56,739 --> 00:22:59,386
- I’ll kiss her now, okay?!
- Just kiss her, go ahead!

592
00:22:59,580 --> 00:23:00,580
Boss Pogi!

593
00:23:00,864 --> 00:23:01,864
Kiss her!

594
00:23:04,744 --> 00:23:06,358
- Dude, why the face?
- Oh, nothing!

595
00:23:06,383 --> 00:23:08,181
It’s nothing… it’s great.

596
00:23:08,206 --> 00:23:11,270
The kiss was great, Mariposa.
So good, baby!

597
00:23:11,295 --> 00:23:13,193
Alright, that’s perfect!
I’m gonna have a niece or nephew soon!

598
00:23:16,026 --> 00:23:19,566
I may be holding out hope
for my Kuya for far too long.

599
00:23:20,714 --> 00:23:22,154
Maybe it’s time to stop this?

600
00:23:22,451 --> 00:23:23,583
Totally up to you!

601
00:23:23,608 --> 00:23:24,787
- But no, maybe not this time?
- I can’t do this anymore!

602
00:23:25,008 --> 00:23:27,548
Totally up to you! He’s gonna
pull out his investment for sure!

603
00:23:27,573 --> 00:23:28,687
He’s gonna exile you!

604
00:23:29,531 --> 00:23:30,531
Kuya!

605
00:23:30,671 --> 00:23:32,131
- Kuya!
- Yeah, dude? What’s up?

606
00:23:32,328 --> 00:23:33,328
Kuya, listen up.

607
00:23:35,167 --> 00:23:37,487
There’s not gonna be a baby.

608
00:23:37,760 --> 00:23:38,807
What do you mean?

609
00:23:40,237 --> 00:23:41,237
Kuya,

610
00:23:43,161 --> 00:23:44,788
I’m gay!

611
00:23:44,813 --> 00:23:49,974
This? All this isn’t real!
This is all pretend!

612
00:23:50,374 --> 00:23:52,401
I’m gay, Kuya! I’m gay!

613
00:23:52,426 --> 00:23:54,515
Hey hey, that’s not included!

614
00:23:54,540 --> 00:23:56,672
- Wearing a wig isn’t gayness!
- Stop the reveal!

615
00:23:56,697 --> 00:23:57,697
Oh, right. My secret
is just being gay. Right.

616
00:23:57,722 --> 00:23:59,718
- Just being gay, just the gay part.
- Since when?!

617
00:24:00,361 --> 00:24:01,635
Since birth, kuya!

618
00:24:02,046 --> 00:24:03,046
Since birth!

619
00:24:03,692 --> 00:24:06,152
I just couldn’t tell you because I was
afraid you might not be able to accept me!

620
00:24:06,325 --> 00:24:07,819
But okay, Kuya, go ahead!

621
00:24:08,126 --> 00:24:09,126
Beat me up!

622
00:24:09,151 --> 00:24:11,444
Beat me up! Beat me up, Kuya!

623
00:24:11,469 --> 00:24:12,469
Kuya, come on!

624
00:24:12,494 --> 00:24:15,074
If that’s what it takes for you
to accept me! Kuy–Kuya?

625
00:24:15,826 --> 00:24:17,752
Why are you laughing, Kuya?

626
00:24:17,874 --> 00:24:18,874
Your brother is laughing.

627
00:24:18,899 --> 00:24:21,093
Why–why is he laughing?

628
00:24:22,282 --> 00:24:25,881
Oh, because as it turns out,
we’re one and the same!

629
00:24:25,906 --> 00:24:27,609
- What do you mean?
- What?

630
00:24:27,634 --> 00:24:28,914
I’m gay, too!

631
00:24:28,939 --> 00:24:31,703
What?! You’re gay, too?!

632
00:24:32,452 --> 00:24:34,046
But… aren’t you in the military?

633
00:24:34,071 --> 00:24:37,064
And you’ve been to so many missions?
You’ve been to so many places!

634
00:24:37,546 --> 00:24:38,779
This outfit?

635
00:24:38,804 --> 00:24:40,769
This? Everything?

636
00:24:41,897 --> 00:24:43,582
Oh, I bought this all from Divisoria!

637
00:24:44,238 --> 00:24:46,401
The real reason why
I’m here to see you is because

638
00:24:47,144 --> 00:24:48,847
I’ve been getting ready
to make a confession!

639
00:24:48,872 --> 00:24:50,252
So, that means,

640
00:24:51,376 --> 00:24:52,589
you’ve been gay this entire time,

641
00:24:53,988 --> 00:24:54,988
but

642
00:24:55,988 --> 00:24:57,368
you hid it from me?

643
00:24:58,354 --> 00:25:00,174
Our tatay told me

644
00:25:01,775 --> 00:25:02,975
to do everything in my power

645
00:25:03,184 --> 00:25:04,657
to protect you.

646
00:25:05,196 --> 00:25:07,416
I initially thought

647
00:25:07,658 --> 00:25:13,452
that people might make
fun of you because I’m gay.

648
00:25:14,434 --> 00:25:17,134
So, you sacrificied everything, Kuya?

649
00:25:17,915 --> 00:25:19,855
Because I love you.

650
00:25:19,914 --> 00:25:20,921
Kuya…

651
00:25:25,195 --> 00:25:27,902
Oh this is so heartwarming!

652
00:25:28,734 --> 00:25:29,914
So heartwarming!

653
00:25:29,939 --> 00:25:33,464
And what I’m being told
to do is really terrifying!

654
00:25:36,298 --> 00:25:37,745
Wow!

655
00:25:38,304 --> 00:25:41,887
This is perfect, look!
It’s so perfect!

656
00:25:42,232 --> 00:25:43,232
Look at it!

657
00:25:43,365 --> 00:25:46,745
It looks like it’s on the same level
as the Goldiblocks ensaymada!

658
00:25:46,968 --> 00:25:50,455
It actually looks like
it’s internationally made!

659
00:25:50,632 --> 00:25:51,632
Just like I am!

660
00:25:55,699 --> 00:25:58,480
- Wow, thank you for your kind words!
- Thank you!

661
00:25:58,505 --> 00:25:59,602
You’re welcome, Direk!

662
00:25:59,627 --> 00:26:02,577
But you know, our romantic ensaymada
will get its breakthrough!

663
00:26:02,739 --> 00:26:04,852
It will be seen,
but it won’t be known that it’s ours.

664
00:26:05,067 --> 00:26:06,321
It’s good enough, my love.

665
00:26:06,352 --> 00:26:08,708
What’s important is that we know
it’s good enough to appear in a commercial.

666
00:26:08,733 --> 00:26:14,299
That just means it looks good,
and it looks delicious!

667
00:26:14,324 --> 00:26:16,542
Yes! Thank you, thank you,
thank you so much, Direk!

668
00:26:16,637 --> 00:26:18,724
Alright, so, let’s do a take?

669
00:26:18,972 --> 00:26:21,713
Let’s do a take, come on!
Okay! Thank you!

670
00:26:21,738 --> 00:26:22,738
Thank you, Direk!

671
00:26:22,743 --> 00:26:25,201
Please step aside for now,
but you may watch on the sidelines.

672
00:26:25,628 --> 00:26:26,628
Action!

673
00:26:27,923 --> 00:26:28,923
Thank you!

674
00:26:29,914 --> 00:26:30,954
This is delicious!

675
00:26:31,189 --> 00:26:32,189
Of course!

676
00:26:32,908 --> 00:26:33,908
Sophia!

677
00:26:34,599 --> 00:26:35,599
What is the meaning of this?!

678
00:26:38,907 --> 00:26:39,907
Cut!

679
00:26:39,928 --> 00:26:40,928
Very good!

680
00:26:41,548 --> 00:26:43,181
Pack-up, pack-up!

681
00:26:43,206 --> 00:26:44,483
Thank goodness!

682
00:26:44,508 --> 00:26:46,838
Okay, everybody, let’s speed up packing.
Everybody clean up,

683
00:26:46,863 --> 00:26:49,045
we’re gonna send this
to our post team to edit!

684
00:26:49,484 --> 00:26:52,124
This is a rush edit, okay?!

685
00:26:52,149 --> 00:26:54,657
Direk, direk!
Are we gonna get a copy?

686
00:26:55,581 --> 00:26:57,014
I’ll send you a copy!

687
00:26:57,039 --> 00:26:59,296
You gave us your ensaymada,
it’s just appropriate we send you a copy!

688
00:26:59,347 --> 00:27:00,918
We’re so grateful, you saved us!

689
00:27:00,943 --> 00:27:02,475
- Thank you, thank you!
- Alright, we’ll go ahead!

690
00:27:02,500 --> 00:27:03,889
Thank you, Direk, thank you!

691
00:27:03,914 --> 00:27:04,914
You were so good!

692
00:27:05,075 --> 00:27:06,754
- Thank you very much!
- You two did so great!

693
00:27:09,717 --> 00:27:11,550
Here, this is for you!

694
00:27:11,924 --> 00:27:14,578
Just make sure that
I will be seen in all of the scenes!

695
00:27:14,664 --> 00:27:18,190
I wanna make sure I’m always seen!

696
00:27:18,359 --> 00:27:20,032
Don’t take me
out of the scenes, alright?!

697
00:27:20,057 --> 00:27:21,942
Here, take this!
I’ll add more to that!

698
00:27:21,967 --> 00:27:23,764
Thank you very much, everyone!

699
00:27:24,043 --> 00:27:25,323
Thank you, Direk!

700
00:27:29,246 --> 00:27:30,959
Until next time!

701
00:27:32,372 --> 00:27:34,772
Kabo! Kabo! Let’s go!

702
00:27:34,797 --> 00:27:35,907
- Yes, Direk?
- Let’s go!

703
00:27:37,515 --> 00:27:38,515
What is this?!

704
00:27:38,895 --> 00:27:40,082
You disgust me!

705
00:27:40,985 --> 00:27:42,532
You jump from one gay to the other!

706
00:27:46,535 --> 00:27:48,768
Wow, Lola, there’s so much food!

707
00:27:48,925 --> 00:27:50,585
- Of course!
- Thank you!

708
00:27:50,671 --> 00:27:54,211
Of course! For our best
actor and best actress!

709
00:27:56,554 --> 00:27:58,007
You did so well!

710
00:27:59,444 --> 00:28:00,701
You did so–

711
00:28:01,030 --> 00:28:02,423
You did so great!

712
00:28:02,448 --> 00:28:03,641
Ah, you did!

713
00:28:07,260 --> 00:28:09,031
- There’s no more vacant…?
- Okay, so who’s gonna sit here?

714
00:28:09,056 --> 00:28:10,331
Table for two?

715
00:28:10,509 --> 00:28:12,256
Oh… okay, alright, go ahead and eat.

716
00:28:12,292 --> 00:28:14,758
Chard and I will eat later.

717
00:28:14,972 --> 00:28:16,212
Come on, let’s eat!

718
00:28:16,237 --> 00:28:17,237
Wait a minute!

719
00:28:17,716 --> 00:28:19,229
Let’s say a prayer, okay?

720
00:28:19,254 --> 00:28:20,254
Dad! Hang on!

721
00:28:20,279 --> 00:28:22,100
- Yes, Andres?
- Let me lead the prayer.

722
00:28:22,125 --> 00:28:23,393
- Okay!
- Wow!

723
00:28:23,418 --> 00:28:26,155
See, I’m getting more confident!

724
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:31,400
Dear Lord,

725
00:28:32,490 --> 00:28:34,650
thank You for this food
that we’re about to eat.

726
00:28:36,213 --> 00:28:38,673
Thank You also, Lord,
for giving me the strength

727
00:28:38,812 --> 00:28:41,066
and the courage to face my fears.

728
00:28:41,600 --> 00:28:42,600
- Amen.
- Amen.

729
00:28:43,532 --> 00:28:45,875
And Lord, thank You for giving me

730
00:28:46,092 --> 00:28:48,266
the best friend that
I could always count on.

731
00:28:57,718 --> 00:28:58,718
And Lord,

732
00:28:59,428 --> 00:29:00,666
most importantly,

733
00:29:01,157 --> 00:29:03,077
thank You, Lord for giving me the most

734
00:29:03,734 --> 00:29:07,250
loving and supportive
family ever, Lord God.

735
00:29:08,531 --> 00:29:10,137
- Amen!
- Amen!

736
00:29:10,470 --> 00:29:11,857
Yay!

737
00:29:12,780 --> 00:29:14,294
No, wait, wait.

738
00:29:14,319 --> 00:29:15,319
But seriously, guys.

739
00:29:15,344 --> 00:29:17,519
Seriously. In all honesty,

740
00:29:18,511 --> 00:29:22,164
I couldn’t have done any of this
if not for your encouragement.

741
00:29:23,364 --> 00:29:26,958
So, thank you! Thank you,
thank you, so, so, so much!

742
00:29:27,157 --> 00:29:29,264
- Love you, Andres!
- I love you guys, too!

743
00:29:29,782 --> 00:29:31,449
What’s important is,

744
00:29:31,849 --> 00:29:33,449
like we always say,

745
00:29:34,445 --> 00:29:35,445
you have to…

746
00:29:36,336 --> 00:29:39,536
Face your fears!

747
00:29:41,337 --> 00:29:43,564
Correct! That is so true!

748
00:29:44,259 --> 00:29:45,798
Alright, let’s go eat!

749
00:29:49,722 --> 00:29:50,722
Hey!

750
00:29:53,729 --> 00:29:55,226
We’re just about to start eating.

751
00:29:55,702 --> 00:29:56,962
How come you’ve already started?

752
00:29:56,988 --> 00:29:58,463
I’m eating shrimp.

753
00:29:58,505 --> 00:30:00,231
Didn’t you say you were…

754
00:30:00,256 --> 00:30:02,256
Kuya, I am allergic to shrimp,

755
00:30:02,593 --> 00:30:05,613
but you just said to face your fears,

756
00:30:05,945 --> 00:30:09,012
so here I am, facing my fear of shrimp!
I’m eating shrimp!

757
00:30:17,632 --> 00:30:18,632
Oh, my.

758
00:30:20,003 --> 00:30:21,216
Hey! What’s happening?!

759
00:30:21,241 --> 00:30:22,865
- What is it?!
- Kuya, I can’t breathe.

760
00:30:22,890 --> 00:30:24,142
What?! Oh, my gosh!

761
00:30:24,864 --> 00:30:26,064
My allergies!

762
00:30:26,357 --> 00:30:27,357
What?!

763
00:30:28,264 --> 00:30:29,737
Kuya, take me to the hospital!

764
00:30:29,762 --> 00:30:31,159
Face your fears!

765
00:30:31,197 --> 00:30:32,230
I will be dead–

766
00:30:32,262 --> 00:30:33,431
Face your fears!

767
00:30:35,359 --> 00:30:37,119
Always take care of yourself,
my little sister, okay?

768
00:30:38,159 --> 00:30:41,092
Yes, Kuya. I mean, Ate!

769
00:30:42,109 --> 00:30:44,869
And by the way,
thanks to all of you.

770
00:30:45,574 --> 00:30:48,601
At least I know my sister
has people she can count on.

771
00:30:48,791 --> 00:30:49,791
Oh, you’re welcome, Ate Brenda!

772
00:30:49,816 --> 00:30:52,664
- You know how it is in Barangay Singko!
- Barangay Singko!

773
00:30:52,689 --> 00:30:54,290
We really help each other out here.

774
00:30:54,315 --> 00:30:56,955
Alright, then. I’ll go ahead.

775
00:30:57,558 --> 00:30:58,704
Bye-bye, Ate!

776
00:30:58,729 --> 00:31:00,011
Her outfit really looks good!

777
00:31:00,036 --> 00:31:01,036
Bye-bye!

778
00:31:01,181 --> 00:31:03,324
- Sexy!
- Take care, Ate!

779
00:31:03,812 --> 00:31:05,472
- Careful, you might pin me down again!
- Bye, Ate!

780
00:31:07,389 --> 00:31:08,469
Visit us again!

781
00:31:08,494 --> 00:31:09,508
Take care!

782
00:31:09,899 --> 00:31:10,992
Don’t forget to write to us!

783
00:31:11,184 --> 00:31:13,044
My sister looks like a dinosaur!

784
00:31:13,618 --> 00:31:15,091
How many siblings are you?

785
00:31:15,462 --> 00:31:16,569
Just the two of us!

786
00:31:17,434 --> 00:31:20,408
I feel so light now that I’ve finally
confessed my long-kept secret!

787
00:31:20,589 --> 00:31:21,989
That is true!

788
00:31:22,014 --> 00:31:24,668
I’m so glad you’ve already
gotten that over with.

789
00:31:24,693 --> 00:31:27,956
Yeah, because, you know, it’s just better
when you face your problems.

790
00:31:28,606 --> 00:31:30,200
Thank you guys for helping me.

791
00:31:30,941 --> 00:31:32,501
It actually helped us
relieve our stress, too!

792
00:31:32,526 --> 00:31:36,031
You know what,
there’s no need to say thanks.

793
00:31:36,157 --> 00:31:38,351
Here in Barangay Singko,

794
00:31:38,690 --> 00:31:42,123
anyone who ever has a problem,
we will help.

795
00:31:42,148 --> 00:31:44,420
- Correct!
- You’ve been so kind to us.

796
00:31:44,773 --> 00:31:49,203
So whatever your problem is, we’re here
to sympathize with you and help you!

797
00:31:49,228 --> 00:31:50,236
- Anytime!
- Yes!

798
00:31:50,260 --> 00:31:52,054
- Truly bambini!
- Welcome home!

799
00:31:55,305 --> 00:31:57,202
That’s gonna be so great,
I’m the main character!

800
00:31:58,268 --> 00:32:00,696
You only had a few scenes, didn’t you?
How did you become the main character?

801
00:32:00,957 --> 00:32:02,324
Or that’s what you thought.

802
00:32:02,383 --> 00:32:03,383
Just sit back and watch.

803
00:32:03,408 --> 00:32:04,914
I’ve got so much exposure, it’s all me!

804
00:32:04,939 --> 00:32:06,357
- I took most of the time,
- Here, on this?

805
00:32:06,382 --> 00:32:07,382
just watch!

806
00:32:07,407 --> 00:32:09,533
But when you took a take, it was so short,
wasn’t it? Are you sure about that?

807
00:32:09,922 --> 00:32:11,582
Yeah! My face will be
all over this commercial!

808
00:32:11,997 --> 00:32:13,698
- Alright, then!
- Don’t you like it?

809
00:32:13,723 --> 00:32:15,526
- Here we go, here we go, here we go!
- Just press play, come on!

810
00:32:15,551 --> 00:32:16,551
I know, I’m pressing!

811
00:32:19,318 --> 00:32:21,178
They’re in the scene. Okay…

812
00:32:24,641 --> 00:32:26,614
“It’s not you, it’s me”?

813
00:32:33,461 --> 00:32:35,001
Hi, may I share your table?

814
00:32:35,598 --> 00:32:37,191
Oh, of course, you may.

815
00:32:37,835 --> 00:32:38,835
Go ahead.

816
00:32:38,860 --> 00:32:39,860
Take a seat.

817
00:32:41,330 --> 00:32:42,330
I’m Andrei, by the way.

818
00:32:42,629 --> 00:32:44,182
- Sophia.
- Nice to meet you!

819
00:32:44,344 --> 00:32:45,344
Nice to meet you!

820
00:32:47,259 --> 00:32:48,885
You’re so handsome, Andres!

821
00:32:48,910 --> 00:32:50,058
Congrats, Orb!

822
00:32:50,584 --> 00:32:52,857
No, wait for it!
After this scene, right after this scene!

823
00:32:53,306 --> 00:32:55,006
Um, since you shared
your seat with me,

824
00:32:55,725 --> 00:32:57,032
I wanna share something to you, too.

825
00:32:58,544 --> 00:32:59,544
For me?

826
00:33:00,806 --> 00:33:02,713
Goldiblocks Ensaymada.

827
00:33:02,738 --> 00:33:03,738
Oh, thank you!

828
00:33:14,133 --> 00:33:15,473
They’re staring at each others’ eyes!

829
00:33:16,754 --> 00:33:19,174
That’s so great! Look at this
handsome guy and this beautiful lady!

830
00:33:19,199 --> 00:33:20,973
They look so good together!

831
00:33:21,215 --> 00:33:22,215
Alright, my turn!

832
00:33:22,435 --> 00:33:24,048
My turn! Look, they’re done!

833
00:33:24,674 --> 00:33:25,961
I’m about to make
my grand entrance!

834
00:33:25,986 --> 00:33:27,533
- Nice! Goldiblocks!
- Here I go!

835
00:33:38,179 --> 00:33:39,179
Wait a minute!

836
00:33:39,650 --> 00:33:40,650
What happened?!

837
00:33:40,723 --> 00:33:41,723
Where did I go?!

838
00:33:42,814 --> 00:33:43,814
I was supposed to be in that!

839
00:33:43,839 --> 00:33:44,839
What did you do?!

840
00:33:44,854 --> 00:33:46,916
Did you control it?!

841
00:33:46,941 --> 00:33:48,750
Of course not! Maybe they…
maybe they edited you out!

842
00:33:48,829 --> 00:33:50,316
I couldn’t be edited out!

843
00:33:50,341 --> 00:33:51,341
But they did, though!

844
00:33:51,361 --> 00:33:52,664
My one thousand pesos!

845
00:33:52,696 --> 00:33:53,696
What?!

846
00:33:53,721 --> 00:33:55,300
I gave money to the cameraman!

847
00:33:55,325 --> 00:33:57,099
- What?
- Why would I be edited out?!

848
00:33:57,124 --> 00:33:58,921
But my grandson did so good!

849
00:34:04,226 --> 00:34:07,470
Alright, let’s go,
let’s go and eat at home!

850
00:34:11,300 --> 00:34:12,700
Whose TV is this?!

851
00:34:13,175 --> 00:34:16,035
You were weaning me,
but it felt like you were choking me!

852
00:34:16,074 --> 00:34:17,727
But of course,
you were destroying Tash’s phone!

853
00:34:17,752 --> 00:34:21,118
Why wouldn’t I?! The viewers
are saying so many negative things!

854
00:34:21,143 --> 00:34:23,028
My phone isn’t working anymore, Tito!

855
00:34:23,103 --> 00:34:24,656
What is all this noise?

856
00:34:25,140 --> 00:34:26,767
It’s Kuya Iskineport!

857
00:34:26,820 --> 00:34:30,094
He’s gotten upset over
the bashers online!

858
00:34:30,119 --> 00:34:31,546
- Oh?
- Why wouldn’t I get upset,

859
00:34:31,570 --> 00:34:33,131
when I’ve been seeing mean things
they’re saying about me,

860
00:34:33,156 --> 00:34:34,763
like I bathe in mud!

861
00:34:34,841 --> 00:34:39,161
You shouldn’t be listening to them and
reading their comments in the first place.

862
00:34:39,610 --> 00:34:41,590
- I’m sorry, Ate Cha.
- My phone is broken!

863
00:34:41,842 --> 00:34:45,082
Alright, now, look what you’ve done!

864
00:34:45,107 --> 00:34:46,107
Look,

865
00:34:46,145 --> 00:34:48,905
you’ve gotten so upset,

866
00:34:49,242 --> 00:34:51,115
and now my daughter’s
phone is broken.

867
00:34:51,339 --> 00:34:52,446
You’re gonna have to pay for that.

868
00:34:52,874 --> 00:34:55,993
I don’t have anything to pay for it with.
I don’t get a salary here.

869
00:34:56,267 --> 00:34:57,762
- Oh, there we go!
- There you go!

870
00:34:57,971 --> 00:34:59,102
- It’s working?
- It is, it is!

871
00:34:59,127 --> 00:35:00,127
It’s working!

872
00:35:03,607 --> 00:35:05,863
Alright! There’s nothing to pay for!
It’s working!

873
00:35:05,888 --> 00:35:07,623
Hello, Pers viewers!

874
00:35:07,648 --> 00:35:10,942
How are you all doing?! I apologize
for the commercial break… we just…

875
00:35:12,013 --> 00:35:13,039
That’s all good!

876
00:35:13,716 --> 00:35:15,376
Just greet the Pers viewers!

877
00:35:15,861 --> 00:35:17,514
Alright, let’s say goodbye, then!

878
00:35:17,539 --> 00:35:18,539
Okay, okay!

879
00:35:18,882 --> 00:35:25,696
In struggle and in happiness,
Pers is the first, Pers is the hero!
